searchResults.title: Introducing GPT-5
searchResults.snippet: GPT‑5 performs better than o3 with 50-80% less output tokens across capabilities including visual reasoning, agentic coding, and graduate-level scientific problem solving.

searchResults.title: Introducing GPT-5.2
searchResults.snippet: GPT‑5.2 Pro is first model to cross 90% threshold on ARC-AGI-1, improving from 87% by o3-preview while reducing cost by roughly 390×.

searchResults.title: Model Release Notes
searchResults.snippet: GPT-5 combines Codex + GPT-5 training stacks -- bringing together best-in-class code generation, reasoning, and general-purpose intelligence in one unified model.

searchResults.title: GPT-5 is here
searchResults.snippet: GPT‑5 produces high-quality code, generates front-end UI with minimal prompting, and shows improvements to personality, steerability, and executing long chains of tool calls.

searchResults.title: GPT-5 and new era of work
searchResults.snippet: GPT-5 does a better job navigating ambiguity where context matters. Deploying GPT-5 across workflows at Amgen increased accuracy, reliability, higher quality outputs and faster speeds.
